OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of a
OL,6,Ffew outbreaks of rain across
OL,7,Fnortheastern Aberdeenshire at first
OL,8,Fthis evening. Otherwise it will be a
OL,9,Fdry night with variable amounts of
OL,10,Fcloud and clear periods.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,13,Fvariable amounts of cloud and sunny
OL,14,Fspells, best of the sunshine later on.
OL,15,FBecoming very warm in sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
